OL,3,CStadium of Light to introduce safe
OL,4,Cstanding for fans
OL,6,FSunderland football club are upgrading
OL,7,Ftheir stadium to include safe standing
OL,8,Ffor fans.
OL,10,FThe development is the latest phase of
OL,11,Fa multi-million pound refurbishment of
OL,12,Fthe Stadium of Light.
OL,14,FThe Championship club will introduce
OL,15,F2,000 standing spaces in the Roker End
OL,16,Fand 1,000 more in the North Upper
OL,17,FStand.
OL,19,FIn addition, a new playing surface and
OL,20,Funder-soil heating system is also
OL,21,Fbeing installed this summer.
