OL,6,FThe Black Cats, who moved to the venue
OL,7,Fon the site of the former
OL,8,FMonkwearmouth Colliery in 1997, claim
OL,9,Fthe investment will have "a
OL,10,Ftransformational impact on the
OL,11,Fmatchday experience".
OL,13,FChairman Kyril Louis-Dreyfus told the
OL,14,Fclub's official website: "We're
OL,15,Fdelighted to announce that we are
OL,16,Fcontinuing a significant period of
OL,17,Finvestment to develop the Stadium of
OL,18,FLight, with the next phase set to
OL,19,Fcomplete before the start of the new
OL,20,Fseason.
